<p>Dear <%= @user_name %>,</p>

<p>
  The Dryad dataset submission you’ve initiated titled, “<%= @resource.title %>” with the
  DOI “<%= @resource.identifier_value %>”, is currently "In Progress". It has not yet been submitted for evaluation
  by a member of our curation team.
</p>

<p>
  If you intend to publish your dataset but are not ready to make it publicly available, select the
  “Keep my dataset Private for Peer Review” option on the final page of the Dryad submission form.
</p>

<p>If your dataset is left “In Progress” for one year without action, it will be deleted.</p>

<p>When you are prepared to submit this dataset for curation and publication, follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li><a href="https://datadryad.org">Login to https://datadryad.org</a></li>
  <li>Click on "My datasets"</li>
  <li>Locate your submission with the status "In Progress"</li>
  <li>Click "Resume" to access your submission</li>
  <li>Incorporate pending edits, if any</li>
  <li>Click "Submit"</li>
</ol>

<p>
  If you do not intend to proceed with the publication of this dataset, you may either select "Delete" from your
  dashboard if this option is available to you, or contact us with your dataset DOI at
  <a href="mailto:<%= @helpdesk_email %>?subject=Withdraw <%= @resource.identifier_value %>"><%= @helpdesk_email %></a>
  to request that it is withdrawn.
</p>
